{ Both sides have castled and the middlegame begins. Black has gained space on the queenside with the advance of the b-pawn and in an ideal world would like to build pressure on the c-file with ...Be6 and ...Rc8. For the time being, that will have to wait. Let's hassle the bishop first. }
