14. Nbd2 Be7 15. Ne1 b6 { Threatening ...Bc5. } 16. Nb3 Kd7
{ The queen's rook enters the game @@StartBracket@@probably on f8 and the king can slide gently to the queenside. With the centre and the bishops, Black stands better. }
