1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 e5 5. Nf3
{ This is not the most threatening reply. Where can the knight go from here? In fact, because it is now Black's move it is possible to take the initiative straight away. }
5... Nf6
