{ If the bishop retreats,  14.Be3  , then Black breaks with  14...d5  , with the advantage. }
14... Bxf6 15. Ndc4 Ne7 16. Ne3 Be6
{ The game is balanced. I would like to improve the position of the dark-squared bishop with ...g6 and ...Bg7, and later ...h5 and ...Bh6. There is also potential to expand on the queenside with ...a6 and ...b5. }
