17. Bc4 Bxc4 18. Nxc4 Qc7 19. Nd6 b6
{ This undermines the knight's support.   It keeps more juice in the position than  19...Qa5+  20.Qd2  Qxc5  21.Nxb7  Rxd2  22.Nxc5  Rxb2  but this endgame should be tenable for White. }
