{ Normally I would exchange off the dark-squared bishop with  13...Bg5  @@StartBracket@@which is also fine for Black@@EndBracket@@ but there is a chance for Black to seize the initiative. }
14. exd5 Ne7
{ gives Black the better pawn structure and there is a threat to play ...Qa5+ winning the d-pawn. }
